query:
INSERT INTO account_properties (
                address,
                miniblock_number,
                preimage_hash,
                versioning_data,
                nonce,
                observable_bytecode_hash,
                bytecode_hash,
                nominal_token_balance,
                bytecode_len,
                artifacts_len,
                observable_bytecode_len
            )
            SELECT
                u.address,
                $1,
                u.preimage_hash,
                u.versioning_data,
                u.nonce,
                u.observable_bytecode_hash,
                u.bytecode_hash,
                u.nominal_token_balance,
                u.bytecode_len,
                u.artifacts_len,
                u.observable_bytecode_len
            FROM
                UNNEST(
                    $2::bytea [],
                    $3::bytea [],
                    $4::numeric [],
                    $5::numeric [],
                    $6::bytea [],
                    $7::bytea [],
                    $8::numeric [],
                    $9::bigint [],
                    $10::bigint [],
                    $11::bigint []
                ) AS u (
                    address,
                    preimage_hash,
                    versioning_data,
                    nonce,
                    observable_bytecode_hash,
                    bytecode_hash,
                    nominal_token_balance,
                    bytecode_len,
                    artifacts_len,
                    observable_bytecode_len
                )
